{"tid":2008553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【靜態技巧】熟讀地圖","createTime":"2020-05-09T06:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T06:30:30.000Z","uid":81167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0cebdce403f5177447ef6a2dddc2d10f691b541","tid":2008553,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"大家冇野做無聊個陣其實可以讀下同記下地圖，做任務嘅時候好多時你都冇時間再拎個地圖出黎check，如果冇個個地區嘅基本概念，係一d緊急嘅時候好易任務失敗。<br />\n<br />\n除左認下方向，邊條路去邊到之外，可以留意下地形嘅高度。係閱讀嘅時候如果需要幫助，可以問google，google d免費野都幾幫得手<br />\n<br />\n桌面版&amp;流動版: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/intl/zh-HK_ALL/earth/versions/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fintl%2Fzh-HK_ALL%2Fearth%2Fversions%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=8f824a82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/intl/zh-HK_ALL/earth/versions/</a>"},{"pid":"0f8eb52fa2ee748eccc8bc09f50f5e803c257078","tid":2008553,"uid":236780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"旺角D路行左10幾年都仲係唔熟路(可能唔鍾意人多既地方)<br />\n但其他地方 上網睇1次地圖就識行<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12d61496e528206bf65141b2687765697d771cf","tid":2008553,"uid":81167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f8eb52fa2ee748eccc8bc09f50f5e803c257078","tid":2008553,"uid":236780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"旺角D路行左10幾年都仲係唔熟路(可能唔鍾意人多既地方)<br />\n但其他地方 上網睇1次地圖就識行<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"有備無患，如果你已經有個一區嘅基本概念，可以閱讀下d橫街小巷，提高你嘅移動速度"},{"pid":"265cdd3156ba2a3a91e8d42596d89e744663cbad","tid":2008553,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"好似背元素表咁"},{"pid":"b6182f778afb08889704660ac87ef20e7d25d5a4","tid":2008553,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"265cdd3156ba2